{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-03003/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-03003"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:30:03"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["extreme close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["overhead"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Numbers are written down on paper."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-03003","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-03003"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/canvas/1/e73d6666-c97e-4c9a-9e35-ff30edc277b6","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T20:34:17.772Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma’s measurements are repeated multiple times both visually and verbally in this scene (in handwriting, on the tape measure, by Reynolds and Cyril). Of course, they need not be, so the choice to do so seems to underscore Alma’s discomfort at being reduced to numbers in this way. This association of women with numbers and their place in the fashion market will occur again <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW103097077 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-04303.html\"><u>later in the film</u></a>.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-03003/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:488.39838492597573,243.47240915208624,596.9313593539705,555.5854643337819"}}}]}]}]}